## Summary of Changes

### Build Configuration Fixes

**`package.json`**:
- Relaxed Node engine constraint from `>=20.19.2` to `>=20.11.0` (environment compatibility)
- Added `react-router-dom@5` as devDependency (required peer dep for `react-router-dom-v5-compat` in tests)

**`webpack.config.ts`**:
- Added `validateSharedModules: false` to `ConsoleRemotePlugin` (SDK 4.21 shared module version mismatches with React 18)
- Added `react/jsx-runtime.js` → `react/jsx-runtime` resolve alias (react-dnd v15 compatibility with React 18)
- Added `InjectMissingLoaders` webpack plugin to work around webpack 5.99's failure to apply `module.rules` loaders to ModuleFederationPlugin container-entry exposed modules (pre-existing issue)

**`jest/config.js`**:
- Fixed `testPathIgnorePatterns` from `/build/` to `<rootDir>/.*/build/` (pre-existing: the broad `/build/` pattern matched the parent directory path, preventing all tests from running)
- Fixed `transformIgnorePatterns` by removing `<rootDir>` prefix (pre-existing: caused test discovery to fail)
- Added React module name mappings to prevent duplicate React instances in tests

### PatternFly 6 API Migration Fixes

**`@patternfly/react-charts` imports** (8 files):
- Changed bare `@patternfly/react-charts` imports to `@patternfly/react-charts/victory` (PF6 restructured chart packages into `victory` and `echarts` sub-packages)
- Updated internal chart paths from `dist/js/components/` to `dist/js/victory/components/` in `tooltip.tsx`

**SCSS/Sass fixes** (14+ files):
- Replaced `@patternfly/patternfly/sass-utilities/all` with `@patternfly/patternfly/sass-utilities` (PF6 removed `_all.scss`, uses `_index.scss`)
- Replaced `@patternfly/patternfly/sass-utilities/colors` imports with CSS custom properties
- Renamed `$pf-v5-global--breakpoint--*` → `$pf-v6-global--breakpoint--*` variables
- Replaced PF5 color SCSS variables with PF6 CSS custom properties

**Component API fixes**:
- `ModalBoxBody`/`ModalBoxFooter` → `ModalBody`/`ModalFooter` (renamed in PF6) in `Modal.tsx`
- Modal `header` prop → `ModalHeader` child component in `create-bs-modal.tsx`
- Modal `actions` prop → `ModalFooter` child component in `selected-capacity.tsx`
- Tabs `isSecondary` prop → `variant="secondary"` in `Tabs.tsx`
- Select `isDisabled` prop removed (moved to MenuToggle) in `multiselectdropdown.tsx`
- Fixed `MultiSelectDropdownProps` type to omit `variant` from `SelectProps` (PF6 narrows variant type)
- `FormGroup` `labelIcon` → `labelHelp` in `file-upload-input.tsx` and `azure-config.tsx`
- `TableData` `style` prop → `className` in `CORSRulesList.tsx` and `LifecycleRulesList.tsx`
- Fixed Dropdown `onSelect` callback signature in `kebab.tsx`
- Fixed `DropdownItem` `onClick` type in `ObjectDetailsSidebar.tsx`
- Fixed `TypeaheadDropdown` `ReactNode` → `string` cast
- Fixed `create-storage-system.tsx` type cast with `as unknown as`
- Fixed `select-replication-type.tsx` destructuring pattern
- Fixed `Element` vs `Element[]` return types in `namespace-step.tsx` and `select-policy-wizard-content.tsx`

